metadata.name: Punk Fighter 1
metadata.description: A collection of 10,000 utility-enabled PFPs that feature rich & unique hand-drawn rare traits. Each Punk unlocks access to P2E game, a members only club and additional benefits the longer you hold them. With a fight club themed metaverse, live streaming of games & token in works; Punks are set to take over the blockchain. Collections release in stages. Visit www.PunkFightClub.io for more details.
